browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over browser:
javascript code executes an event handler
(onsubmit) that creates a new note from
input value and add this to the notes list
rerendering the note list on the page
and sending it to the server
end note

server->browser: { "message": "note created" }

note over server:
server receives data
server stores the data in data.json
server sends json-message
and doesn't ask for a redirect
end note
